curam.util.common.domain
Interface DomainNames.Root

All Known Subinterfaces:
DomainNames.Core
Enclosing interface:
DomainNames
public static interface DomainNames.Root

Root domains do not share a common ancestor domain and provide the base from which all other domains are derived directly or indirectly. Root domains are supported by the core infrastructure.
